- Allow behavior options to be passed in the Hash-based configuration mode
- Create a behavior which replies with the sent data; use in integration test for speed
- Remove some duplication / clarify the Configuration class as needed
- Dynamically create new behaviors like "SlowResponseForEachLine" by using Module.const_missing
- Log every request to the server/behavior, in addition to open, close
- Use ActiveSupport or other extensions for time durations (seconds, minutes, etc.)
